snippet.title: Gravitas Demo - a gravity toy
snippet.description:
This is a simple demonstration of my app for Android called Gravitas - a physics and gravity toybox. This new version (1.0) features a new toy called Rock Tumbler, new music, new menus and more sound effects. More toys and features are in the works! Check out the Google Play page for more info: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.BrainBlinks.Gravitas

Video, music and sound recorded via camcorder from my Nexus 7 tablet.
